text: Falsestoloides is a genus of longhorn beetles of the subfamily Lamiinae.Biolib.cz - Falsestoloides. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==Species== The genus contains the following species: * Falsestoloides mexicana Breuning, 1954 * Falsestoloides tubericollis Breuning, 1980 ==References== Category:Desmiphorini
